data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Priced under market value. There is still time to celebrate Christmas in your new home!!  Here is a rare opportunity to own in the sought after Candlelight Village.  This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath pool home is a must see.   Enter through the foyer to the large open family/living room. Open kitchen with combined dining room with wood burning fireplace that leads to a beautiful screened pool area. Master bathroom with shower and access to pool area. Split floor plan. Located close to downtown Brooksville and perfect for an easy commute to Tampa.
